# Local-only coordination directories — not committed.
# presence/: per-agent heartbeat JSON, written every 30s by the supervisor.
#            Read by same-machine peers to check if an agent is live.
# wake/:     transient signal files, written by the supervisor after a push
#            when a recipient's mailbox changed. Recipients poll for this file
#            every 1s while idle and wake immediately when it appears.
#            Also written by wake-listen.ts when a Supabase Realtime broadcast
#            arrives for this agent.
presence/
wake/
